snippet.title: Aliens  Redacted Trailer
snippet.description:
A retro style shooter set in the Alien Universe.

Explore the ruins of a derelict Engineer ship as you try to uncover what happened to the crew of the prisoner transport USS Boethiah after it crash landed on the planet. 

Game Page: https://tinyurl.com/thwbu8bp

Music Thanks to https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/
